{{Set(name="schema", value=_orderKeeperSchemasSkill(promise="True"))}}

{{#system~}}Based on the agent's <LastReply> determine if the agent is actively promising to add an item to the order or submit the order.

**Guidelines for setting "promised"**:
1. Set "promised" to `true` if the agent explicitly states that *they themselves* will add an item to the user's order or submit their order.
  - Examples:
    - "Give me a moment, I’ll enter your order into the system..."
    - "...I will submit your order now..."
    - "I will submit your pick up / delivery order now."
    - "I'm submitting your pick up / delivery order..."
Be careful not to set as promised if the agent stated that they are already added item / submitted the order.
2. Set "promiseTarget" to the corresponding action the agent is commited to do.

**Note:** The Agent can talk in different languages.

---

<LastReply>
{{agentAnswer}}
</LastReply>

---

JSON object:{{~/system}}

{{Set(name="promise", value=Gen(jsonSchema=schema, validateSchema="True", temperature=0.2, topP=0, thinkingBudget=85))}}

{{#if GetValueJSON(obj=promise, key="promised") == "true"}}
  {{Set(name="promiseTarget", value=Stringify(GetValueJSON(obj=promise, key="promiseTarget")))}}
  {{Set(name="askedToWait", value=GetValueJSON(obj=promise, key="askedToWait"))}}
  {{#if promiseTarget == "submit_order"}}
    {{_submitOrderSkill(userId=userId, agentAnswer=agentAnswer, memory=memory)}}
    {{Return()}}
  {{/if}}
  {{#if promiseTarget == "enter_order"}}
    {{#if askedToWait == "true"}}
      {{_checkOrderSkill(userId=userId, agentAnswer=agentAnswer, memory=memory, askedToWait="True")}}
    {{else}}
      {{_checkOrderSkill(userId=userId, agentAnswer=agentAnswer, memory=memory)}}
    {{/if}}
    {{Return()}}
  {{/if}}
{{/if}}
